
 	*******************************
 	*     TorDNS LocalProxy       *
  	*   How to torify Windows     *
	*******************************
 
This program allows to connect through Tor network 
without a SOCKS proxy support.
 
It replaces the DNS server and create a proxy for each request 
to the DNS addresses tor.

        1) Configure TorDNS
        2) Run tor
	3) Run java -jar tordns.jar
	4) Set dns to: 127.0.0.1 127.0.0.2
	
